{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"### Root Cause","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053131472Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"The DSL parser stores prompt/script values with `file(\"...\")` wrapper syntax (e.g. `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`), but the `handleAPIStepContent` handler was using this raw value directly as a file path, causing the file read to fail.","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053136372Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053164435Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"Additionally, the handler checked `step.Config[\"command\"]` but the DSL uses `\"run\"` as the key.","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053169835Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053180806Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"### Files Changed","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053191536Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053196646Z"}
