{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"   - Added `extractFilePath()` helper that unwraps `file(\"path\")` → `path`","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053210672Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"   - Fixed prompt file reading to use `extractFilePath(prompt)` before building the file path","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053288299Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"   - Changed `step.Config[\"command\"]` → `step.Config[\"run\"]` to match the DSL key","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053307055Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"   - Applied same `extractFilePath()` to the script path handling","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053318386Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053323536Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"2. **`internal/adapters/web/templates/project_detail.html`**:","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053327954Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"   - Added `\"run\"` to the displayed config keys in the step drawer (alongside existing `\"command\"`)","timestamp":"2026-03-09T00:43:36.053342612Z"}
